### POST /api/v1/drivers/location
### Descripción: Enviar ubicación del conductor. Requiere rol Driver o Admin.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>
### Códigos: 200 OK | 400 { "error", "code" }

# @name driverLocation
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/drivers/location
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "latitude": 19.4326,
  "longitude": -99.1332,
  "heading": 90,
  "speed": 0
}

### Response esperado (200): (sin body)
### Response error (400): { "error", "code" }
